</select></form></div></div><div id="inner"><div class="wrap"><div id="content-sidebar-wrap"><div id="content" class="hfeed"><div class="recent-post-listing"><div class="one-half first"><h4>Top Healthcare Story</h4></div><div class="one-half"><h4>Latest Healthcare News</h4></div><div class="left one-half first"><div class="post"><p class="image"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/decreased-viral-infection/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/93698174-303x174.jpg" /></a></p><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/decreased-viral-infection/">How one facility decreased viral infection rates in children by 44%</a></h2><p>This year&#8217;s difficult flu season is almost over &#8211; and there&#8217;s more good news where that came from. A new&hellip;<a class="more-link" href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/decreased-viral-infection/">Click to continue</a></p></div></div><div class="right one-half"><div class="post"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/data-patient-placement/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/172588046-56x56.jpg" /></a><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/data-patient-placement/">Use data analytics to maximize patient placement</a></h2></div><div class="post"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/suicide-in-hospitals-why-ligature-is-2018s-regulatory-heavy-hitter/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/GettyImages-503494586-56x56.jpg" /></a><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/suicide-in-hospitals-why-ligature-is-2018s-regulatory-heavy-hitter/">Suicide in hospitals: Why ligature is 2018’s regulatory heavy hitter</a></h2></div><div class="post"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/net-neutrality-repeal/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/ThinkstockPhotos-200470360-001-56x56.jpg" /></a><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/net-neutrality-repeal/">Net neutrality repeal will affect your hospital: Learn how</a></h2></div><div class="post"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/reduce-pneumonia-rates/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/GettyImages-512098822-56x56.jpg" /></a><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/reduce-pneumonia-rates/">Reduce pneumonia rates, save money: Strategies for your facility</a></h2></div></div><div class="bottom"><div class="one-third post first"><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/medication-adherence/">How your hospital can improve medication adherence</a></h2></div><div class="one-third post"><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/why-cloud-will-be-healthcares-hero-in-2018/">Why cloud will be health care’s hero in 2018</a></h2></div><div class="one-third post last"><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/6-patient-safety-issues/">6 patient safety issues your hospital must address</a></h2></div></div></div><div class="content-ticker"><ul class="slides"></ul></div><div class="popular-posts-listing"><h4>Popular Healthcare Articles</h4><div class="post no-image"><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/the-12-most-debilitating-diseases/">The 12 Most Debilitating Diseases</a></h2><p>Debilitating diseases come in many shapes and forms &#8211; from those that attack the muscles in our body and affect our physical abilities to those that affect our brain function and impair our thought processes.</p>
<p class="more"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/the-12-most-debilitating-diseases/" class="square-button">Click to continue</a></p></div><div class="post no-image"><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/the-25-most-beautiful-hospital-designs-in-the-world/">The 25 Most Beautiful Hospitals in the World</a></h2><p>Hospital architecture and designs have transformed over time,  from the once sterile white walls and stark decor to vibrant colors and eye-catching materials on the interior and exterior. The elements in today’s best designs have been proven to improve patient &hellip;</p>
<p class="more"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/the-25-most-beautiful-hospital-designs-in-the-world/" class="square-button">Click to continue</a></p></div><div class="post"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/communication-patient-harm/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/ThinkstockPhotos-82635633-134x134.jpg" /></a><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/communication-patient-harm/">How communication problems put patients, hospitals in jeopardy</a></h2><p>Communication is important in providing top quality patient care. Any breakdowns in communication can lead to serious problems, such as patient complications or deaths. A new report shows just how much poor communication impacts hospital care. </p>
<p class="more"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/communication-patient-harm/" class="square-button">Click to continue</a></p></div></div><h4 class="with-arrow">Category Articles</h4><div class="category-posts-listing"><div class="top left cat-listing category-15"><h5><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/category/hospital-management/">Hospital Management</a></h5><p class="image"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/leadership-rounds-staff-engagement/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/465899655-1-309x97.jpg" /></a></p><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/leadership-rounds-staff-engagement/">Leadership rounds promote staff engagement</a></h2><p>All hospital leaders need to see what&#8217;s happening at your facility. Leadership rounds are a&hellip;</p>
<ul><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/accountability-no-excuse/">Keys to fostering a &#8216;no excuse&#8217; culture of accountability at your hospital</a></li><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/population-health-management-focusing-your-facilitys-efforts/">Population health management: Focusing your facility&#8217;s efforts</a></li><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/just-culture/">Create a &#8216;just culture&#8217; in your hospital &#038; revamp patient care</a></li></ul></div><div class="top right cat-listing category-10"><h5><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/category/finance/">Finance</a></h5><p class="image"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/3-steps-to-improved-insurance-follow-up/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/GettyImages-87507596-309x97.jpg" /></a></p><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/3-steps-to-improved-insurance-follow-up/">3 steps to improved insurance follow-up</a></h2><p>Changes in the healthcare industry have put hospital administrators in a tough spot. They must&hellip;</p>
<ul><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/total-cost-of-care/">What your hospital should know when measuring total cost of care</a></li><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/patients-financial-info/">Survey: Patients want financial info before treatment</a></li><li><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/bundled-payments-next/">Big changes to bundled payments: What to expect next</a></li></ul></div><hr /><div class="bottom left cat-listing category-2780"><h5><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/category/healthcare-it/">Healthcare IT</a></h5><p class="image"><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/how-to-promote-accessibility-in-healthcare-cybersecurity/"><img src="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/wp-content/uploads/GettyImages-516794972-309x97.jpg" /></a></p><h2><a href="http://www.healthcarebusinesstech.com/how-to-promote-accessibility-in-healthcare-cybersecurity/">How to promote accessibility in healthcare cybersecurity</a></h2><p>The more accessible healthcare information is, the more value it provides to patients and providers&hellip;</p>
